room_title: Escape room "Death Row" by Headless Horseman Escape Rooms in Ulster Park
room_description: Death Row houses the most horrific criminals, including Prisoner X the only inmate to vanish without a trace. Now you and your fellow inmates have the same goal. Can you execute your plan to rewire the electric chair and escape? There is only one problem... one of you must sacrifice yourself in the electric chair to pull this escape off.
